---
// HistoryPanel component for displaying conversation history
---

<div class="panel-card">
  <!-- Panel Header -->
  <div class="panel-section-header">
    <h3 class="panel-title">Chat History</h3>
    <p class="panel-subtitle">Your recent conversations</p>
  </div>

  <div class="panel-divider"></div>

  <!-- History Content -->
  <div class="journal-entries-container" id="history-container">
    <!-- Sample conversations -->
    <div class="journal-entry-card conversation-item" data-date="2025-08-23" data-keywords="anxiety morning breathing meditation">
      <div class="journal-entry-header">
        <div class="journal-entry-date">
          <div class="journal-date-day">23</div>
          <div class="journal-date-month">Aug</div>
        </div>
        <div class="journal-entry-meta">
          <h4 class="journal-entry-title">Morning Anxiety & Breathing</h4>
          <div class="journal-entry-info">
            <span class="journal-entry-time">Today, 2:30 PM</span>
            <span class="section-count">18 messages</span>
            <span class="section-count">22 min</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="journal-entry-content">
        We discussed your morning anxiety patterns and explored breathing techniques. You mentioned feeling overwhelmed when waking up, and we worked through a 4-7-8 breathing exercise that seemed to help calm your nervous system.
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-2">
          <span class="filter-chip">anxiety</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">morning routine</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">breathing</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="journal-entry-card conversation-item" data-date="2025-08-22" data-keywords="goals motivation productivity sleep">
      <div class="journal-entry-header">
        <div class="journal-entry-date">
          <div class="journal-date-day">22</div>
          <div class="journal-date-month">Aug</div>
        </div>
        <div class="journal-entry-meta">
          <h4 class="journal-entry-title">Goals & Evening Routine</h4>
          <div class="journal-entry-info">
            <span class="journal-entry-time">Yesterday, 7:45 PM</span>
            <span class="section-count">31 messages</span>
            <span class="section-count">38 min</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="journal-entry-content">
        Long conversation about setting realistic goals and improving productivity. We created a personalized evening routine to help with sleep quality and discussed strategies for maintaining motivation during challenging periods.
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-2">
          <span class="filter-chip">goal setting</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">motivation</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">sleep routine</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="journal-entry-card conversation-item" data-date="2025-08-20" data-keywords="stress work boundaries mindfulness">
      <div class="journal-entry-header">
        <div class="journal-entry-date">
          <div class="journal-date-day">20</div>
          <div class="journal-date-month">Aug</div>
        </div>
        <div class="journal-entry-meta">
          <h4 class="journal-entry-title">Work Stress & Boundaries</h4>
          <div class="journal-entry-info">
            <span class="journal-entry-time">August 20, 4:15 PM</span>
            <span class="section-count">24 messages</span>
            <span class="section-count">29 min</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="journal-entry-content">
        Discussion about work stress and setting healthy boundaries. We explored mindfulness techniques for managing overwhelming workdays and practiced a brief body scan meditation together.
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-2">
          <span class="filter-chip">work stress</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">boundaries</span>
          <span class="filter-chip">mindfulness</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
